              <p class="text-1xl text-white">Detect and classify objects in images</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h1 class="text-2xl text-white">Semantic Annotation</h1>
              <p class="text-1xl text-white">Classify each pixel  of an image  into predefined categories</p>
