          execution and relieving you from time management concerns.
        </div>
      </div>
      <!-- 3. -->
      <div class="number-card flex-row space-x-2 text-center space-y-2">
        <div class="flex flex-row gap-2 justify-center items-center ">
          <div class="">03.</div>
          <div class="text-gray-300 tab-mov">Annotators Coordination<span class="bottom-line"></span></div>
        </div>
